---
title: Speedy Turkey Bolognese with cheese and cherry tomatoes
description: Bolognese is a meat-based sauce that gets its name from the city of Bologna. Though most often cooked using beef mince, this version relies on turkey for a leaner form of protein.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R25_W40_IE_IEXQT18825-2_Main_high-6da9046c.jpg
